{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 132925, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "团委老师宁来啦", "timestamp": 1594781538, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 132932, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我可不敢冒充团委老师，冒充老师是要封号的（逃", "timestamp": 1594781591, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 132933, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可还有一些问题。如果禁止名字/名字缩写，那也同时禁止了对公众人物的讨论，这个范围需要认真界定下吧。", "timestamp": 1594781594, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 132938, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 禁止的是人身攻击，而不是禁止所有提到名字的内容", "timestamp": 1594781636, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 132965, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为什么“人身攻击”与事实无关呢？（不懂就问", "timestamp": 1594781807, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 132970, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 就是说无论事实如何都不应该人身攻击", "timestamp": 1594781860, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 132977, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 意思是，根据普遍理解，就算说的是真的，也属于人身攻击的范畴", "timestamp": 1594781930, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 132979, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 如果是假的，那就属于侮辱诽谤了", "timestamp": 1594781954, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 132995, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 这逻辑哪里来的，事实也不允许说了？只要不涉及隐私，为什么不能说？", "timestamp": 1594782165, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 132999, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这种规则容易被无限放大", "timestamp": 1594782206, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 133000, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那岂不是树洞上几乎不能有一点点对个人的批评了？", "timestamp": 1594782224, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 133010, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "简直是苏联笑话复刻，”我只是把他们做的得事情说出来“", "timestamp": 1594782347, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 133017, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 老滑坡了", "timestamp": 1594782415, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 133075, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是您构想的规则不太现实、不合理；人身攻击是带有恶的目的性的，就以您举的例子而言，对他人现状事实的一些批评至少在平台应当是允许的，至少树洞本意是一个说话的地方。当然，您提出的建议本意肯定是好的，我也觉得对有些人的评价不宜，但这绝不应该直接通过硬性规定的办法来解决，您对该条的解释确有过分，请您三思。", "timestamp": 1594783122, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 133153, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 那么至少 带着脏字的骂人已经超出批评的范围了吧？", "timestamp": 1594783861, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 133169, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 如果是 xxx x你老母这种，即使是名字缩写也显然违反七.4，肯定会被删啊", "timestamp": 1594784006, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 133178, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: “傻逼”这种算不算呢？如果算，那么很可惜的是并没有被删", "timestamp": 1594784069, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 133187, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 22892, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 那肯定得算啊…", "timestamp": 1594784267, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 1, "pid": 22892, "reply": 18, "tag": "树洞管理相关", "text": "# 树洞管理相关\n\n希望管理员依照规范禁止实名挂人行为。\n\n根据T大树洞运营规范第七（4）条：\n\n> 七、 用户不得利用T大树洞上传、发布、传播如下干扰T大树洞正常运营，或者侵害其他用户或第三方合法权益，或者经举报、申诉并核实准确的内容：\n> 4. 含有侮辱诽谤、人身攻击、虚假信息等内容，对他人或机构造成不良影响的；\n\n含有实名信息（姓名、姓名缩写或其他可确定个人身份的信息）的挂人应当属于对他人造成不良影响的人身攻击。\n\n人身攻击是与事实无关的，无论攻击的内容是否属实，只要攻击、批评对方个人因素相关之断言或质疑；如人格、动机、态度、地位、阶级或处境等，都属于人身攻击的范畴。", "timestamp": 1594781482, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782592, "url": "", "vote": {}}}